    #[doc = "Unloads a module\nUnloads a module `hmod` from the current context. Attempting to unload\na module which was obtained from the Library Management API such as\n::cuLibraryGetModule will return ::CUDA_ERROR_NOT_PERMITTED.\n\n# Arguments\n\n* `hmod` - - Module to unload\n\n# Returns\n\n::CUDA_SUCCESS,\n::CUDA_ERROR_DEINITIALIZED,\n::CUDA_ERROR_NOT_INITIALIZED,\n::CUDA_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT,\n::CUDA_ERROR_INVALID_VALUE,\n::CUDA_ERROR_NOT_PERMITTED\n\\notefnerr \\note_destroy_ub # See also\n\n> [`::cuModuleGetFunction,`]\n::cuModuleGetGlobal,\n::cuModuleGetTexRef,\n::cuModuleLoad,\n::cuModuleLoadData,\n::cuModuleLoadDataEx,\n::cuModuleLoadFatBinary"]
