    #[doc = "Get stream resources\nGet the `type` resources available to the `hStream` and store them in `resource.`\nNote: The API will return ::CUDA_ERROR_INVALID_RESOURCE_TYPE is `type` is\n`CU_DEV_RESOURCE_TYPE_WORKQUEUE_CONFIG` or `CU_DEV_RESOURCE_TYPE_WORKQUEUE.`\n\n# Arguments\n\n* `hStream` - - Stream to get resource for\n* `resource` - - Output pointer to a CUdevResource structure\n* `type` - - Type of resource to retrieve\n\n# Returns\n\n::CUDA_SUCCESS,\n::CUDA_ERROR_DEINITIALIZED,\n::CUDA_ERROR_NOT_INITIALIZED,\n::CUDA_ERROR_INVALID_RESOURCE_TYPE,\n::CUDA_ERROR_INVALID_VALUE,\n::CUDA_ERROR_INVALID_HANDLE\n\\notefnerr # See also\n\n> [`::cuGreenCtxCreate,`]\n::cuGreenCtxStreamCreate,\n::cuStreamCreate,\n::cuDevSmResourceSplitByCount,\n::cuDevResourceGenerateDesc,\n::cudaStreamGetDevResource"]
